		"name": "ImpactBoard GitHub App API",
		"description": "Complete API collection for the ImpactBoard GitHub App.\n\nImpactBoard is a GitHub App that provides contribution analytics, leaderboards, and README automation for organizations.\n\n## Authentication\n\n- **Webhooks**: Authenticated via GitHub webhook signature (HMAC SHA-256)\n- **Public Endpoints**: Rate-limited but no authentication required\n- **README API**: Rate-limited by organization\n\n## Base URL\n\nSet the `{{baseUrl}}` variable to your deployment URL (e.g., `http://localhost:3000` for local development).\n\n## Rate Limits\n\n| Endpoint Category | Limit |\n|-------------------|-------|\n| Public Badges | 100 requests/15 min |\n| Webhooks | 100 requests/15 min |\n| README Update | 10 requests/hour/org |",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "impactboard"
	},
